text: Oleksiy Oleksiyovych Bykov (; born 29 March 1998) is a Ukrainian football player. He plays for FC Mariupol. ==Club career== He made his Ukrainian Premier League debut for FC Mariupol on 18 March 2018 in a game against FC Shakhtar Donetsk. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:People from Khartsyzk Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:Ukraine under-21 international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:FC Mariupol players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players
